      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. The engine is very difficult to start, frequently stalls, and there are several significant fluid leaks that require immediate attention. Cosmetically, the body shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust, multiple dents, and faded paint. The interior also requires a deep clean and repair of several torn surfaces. This car is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
