    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and truly looks like it just rolled off the assembly line. It has been meticulously maintained and cared for, offering a flawless driving experience and a spotless interior that still feels brand new. This is a rare find for anyone seeking perfection on wheels!",
